Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agents are pleased to present 21 Cooper Street, Paddington. This three-storey brick apartment block comprising 5 x 2 bedroom oversized units is positioned in a highly sought-after location which is set to capitalise on the substantial demand in the Sydney City Fringe property market. The property provides prospective buyers a secure income in a strong leasing market with the opportunity to further value-add through refurbishment, rental reversion and strata subdivision.

21 Cooper Street, Paddington benefits from the following key attributes:

- 5 x large 2 bedroom apartment block
- Land area of 449sqm* with NSA of 382sqm* (internal area)
- Strong passing income
- Secure investment with refurbishment potential
- Potential rental reversion and strata subdivision opportunity
- First time offered to market in 50 years
- Short walk to Paddington's exclusive 'Five Ways' providing direct access to Sydney CBD
- North facing apartments flooded with natural light

21 Cooper Street, Paddington will be sold via public auction on Tuesday, 29nd October 2019 at 10.30am at AuctionWORKS.

For more information on this property please contact the exclusive agents. 

*Approximate
Note: All financial figures have been provided by the Vendor. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own independent due diligence.
